MVD Russia is proposing to tighten the law in relation to the owners of civilian weapons.
It is a reaction of the government authorities to recent events: the incitement was the shooting at weddings that took place without victims, and the massacre prepared by Moscow lawyer Dimitri Vinogradov, which resulted in the death of seven people.
