But here it is necessary to ask where it comes from.
If it is from other EU countries, then poverty will move from one country to another, or it will not come at all, because Chinese, Indian, Brazilian, Turkish, Moroccan, Egyptian or African still work for a fraction of the European wage.
This applies to the whole of Latin America.
